# Copy to .env.local to enable real Google sign-in + database (via Supabase).
# Leave unset to use the built-in mock login with local-only storage.
#
# Get these from your Supabase project: Settings -> API.
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL       = Project URL (https://<ref>.supabase.co)
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  = the public "anon" key (safe to expose; RLS protects data)
#
# Full setup (project, DB migration, Google OAuth) is in docs/SETUP-SUPABASE.md.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
